üìë Technical Compliance Artifacts This section consolidates all technical documentation (.md files) detailing the requirements, controls, and criteria for each certification mandated by the project. All files below are version-controlled, fully auditable, and automatically consumed by the CI/CD pipeline, ensuring traceability, evidence generation, and continuous validation.

