üåê Multilingual Interface
All internal interface strings, comments, and developer-facing texts are written in English. Only client-facing content remains in Portuguese ‚Äî and is automatically translated via the language selector (üáßüá∑/üá∫üá∏) powered by the Brachat Translator module.

CI/CD Pipeline includes:

‚úÖ Linting & Formatting: ESLint, Prettier

‚úÖ SAST: Semgrep, SonarCloud

‚úÖ Dependency Scans: Snyk, OWASP DC

‚úÖ DAST: OWASP ZAP

‚úÖ Container Scans: Trivy, Dockle

‚úÖ Secrets Detection: Gitleaks, Semgrep, TruffleHog

‚úÖ Test Suites: Unit, Integration, Security (Jest, Pytest, JUnit)

‚úÖ Audit Logging: Hash + timestamped logs

‚úÖ Branch Protection / CODEOWNERS enforced

‚úÖ Public Artifact Publication (SOC2 & M&A readiness)

‚úÖ Badges: Quality Gate, Coverage, Vulnerability status

