4 ‚Ä¢ Compliance Coverage
Framework / Norm	Controls Met
ISO 31000	Risk assessment & treatment
ISO 27005	Info-security risk analysis
SOX ¬ß404	Monitoring of legal internal controls
SOC 2 (PI, Security)	Logging, integrity, traceability
ESG (SASB / GRI 419)	Socio-economic & governance compliance
5 ‚Ä¢ Technical Architecture (High-Level)
Data Harvester ‚Äî collects gazettes, LexML, higher-court repos (XML / HTML)
Embedding Pipeline ‚Äî Sentence-BERT legal fine-tune + Pinecone vectors
Graph DB (Neo4j) ‚Äî links norms, decisions, entities (company, sector, jurisdiction)
Risk Engine (Python + Pandas) ‚Äî computes probability √ó impact, outputs JSON-LD
Explainable Layer ‚Äî GPT-NeoX fine-tuned, white-box justifications
Dashboard / API ‚Äî React + GraphQL, XBRL / CSV export for GRC ERPs
