7 ‚Ä¢ Limitations & Risk Register
No personalised legal opinion ‚Äî output is analytic; final judgement by counsel.
Corpus dependency ‚Äî insight quality tied to data completeness; continual scraping required.
Explainability trade-off ‚Äî deeper models may obscure transparency; mitigated with LIME / SHAP.
8 ‚Ä¢ Roadmap (T-0 ‚Üí T + 12 m)
Q	Milestone	KPI
Q0	Pilot (3 multinationals) + federal courts	Litigation coverage ‚â• 90 %
