üè• BTHealth ‚Äì Healthcare Compliance & Patient-Data Governance
Use case
Multi-framework clinical-data governance (HIPAA, LGPD-Sa√∫de, ISO 27799) that stores every EHR event on an immutable ledger and exposes transparency dashboards for patients and regulators ‚Äî 100 % SaaS, zero on-prem hardware.

